00:02:15.844 --> 00:02:17.762 position:50% align:center
Yet again, I'm back on a
Panty Quest to find true love.

00:02:17.846 --> 00:02:20.265 position:50% align:center
Come on, I don't have time
to keep sniffing around.

00:02:20.348 --> 00:02:22.267 position:50% align:center
I need to take care of
another important mission!

00:02:22.350 --> 00:02:23.184 position:50% align:center
