be invisible to them.

00:02:39.075 --> 00:02:40.285 position:50% align:center
Just as planned!

00:02:40.368 --> 00:02:42.871 position:50% align:center
All part of Operation:
Koharu Is a First-Year.

00:02:42.954 --> 00:02:45.915 position:50% align:center
